刚看了一眼bootstrap，貌似还是有一层row的处理，它的row还是有高度的，把container撑起来。</span><ul class="reply-wrap"><li class="reply"style="display:block;" data-id=381><p class="reply-info"><a href="/user/profile?userId=10899">大家好我是冇</a>&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<span class="time">03-22 14:46</span></p><p class="reply-content">container里面直接清除浮动就不会高度塌缩了。<br />
row的作用说错了，row是用来保证下一行的内容不会因为浮动挤在上一行末尾的。</p></li><li class="reply" data-id=207><p class="reply-info">作者<a href="/user/profile?userId=4233">张睿武</a>&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<span class="time">03-19 10:36</span></p><p class="reply-content">多谢提建议，当时写的时候也考虑过row，以前用过bootstrap，但是想从简一下，就没用，等我修改修改！</p></li><li class="show-more"><button class="more-btn btn btn-link">显示全部（共<em>2</em>条评论）</button></li></ul></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="401"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=286" target="_blank">SHSF</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-16 21:00</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=914" target="_blank">周鹏</a>&nbsp;03-16 21:01&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">5</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">响应式布局的话，怎么能够不加禁止缩放呢，不加禁止缩放，当你切换到手机时，需要重新刷新，重新进行http请求，才可以看到效果啊！而且大家普遍都没有写啊！可以在&lt;head&gt;处加上&lt;meta name=&quot;viewport&quot; content=&quot;width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no&quot; /&gt;啊！</span><ul class="reply-wrap"><li class="reply"style="display:block;" data-id=70><p class="reply-info">作者<a href="/user/profile?userId=4233">张睿武</a>&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<span class="time">03-17 12:51</span></p><p class="reply-content">因为是一个小任务，所以没考虑这么多，如果是比较完整的项目话会注意head部分的，谢谢指正！！</p></li></ul></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="345"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=1069" target="_blank">小白向前冲</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-16 11:38</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=2435" target="_blank">王贤</a>&nbsp;03-16 11:38&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">8</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">一个文档只要一个固定的box-sizing，不要在单独的元素上控制box-sizing。<br />
